      "message": "this leaves m_extraInfo un-initialized which is a bad idea in general. You should probably define this with default values and inlined constructors like:\n\n  struct GenNameInfo {\n      ObjectNameType m_type \u003d 0;\n      union { .. } m_extraInfo \u003d {};\n\n      GenNameInfo() \u003d delete;\n      explicit GenNameInfo(NameObjectType type) : m_type(type) {}\n      explicit GenNameInfo(ShaderType shaderType)\n          : m_type(SHADER), m_extraInfo({.shaderType \u003d shaderType }) {}\n  };",
